00:35:55,390 --> 00:35:56,710
it's just our guess.

579
00:35:57,430 --> 00:35:58,960
We have no actual evidence.

580
00:35:59,310 --> 00:36:01,440
And I don't want to take revenge on you.

581
00:36:01,750 --> 00:36:03,550
I just want to change something.

582
00:36:04,790 --> 00:36:06,270
What do you want?

583
00:36:07,150 --> 00:36:08,390
Our key

584
00:36:09,270 --> 00:36:10,590
is with that monster.

585
00:36:10,840 --> 00:36:11,840
We want that back.

586
00:36:13,070 --> 00:36:15,070
You can even abandon your daughter.

587
00:36:15,190 --> 00:36:18,430
Can't you admit that she is a monster?

588
00:36:20,430 --> 00:36:21,760
Why not?

589
00:36:24,110 --> 00:36:26,670
I can't control her.

590
00:36:27,310 --> 00:36:29,590
No one can control her.

591
00:36:30,030 --> 00:36:31,690
We're willing to give it a try.

592
00:36:32,590 --> 00:36:34,070
The taboo condictions

593
00:36:34,310 --> 00:36:36,030
that Madame has lured us.

594
00:36:37,270 --> 00:36:39,990
Don't enter the temple alone. Don't look at the well in a pair.

595
00:36:39,990 --> 00:36:43,190
Don't hold the tree as a trio. Don't lean on the rail alone.

596
00:36:43,870 --> 00:36:44,870
Xiong Qi, Ke.

597
00:36:55,670 --> 00:36:59,030
Jiu. Jiu.

598
00:37:01,390 --> 00:37:02,390
You three

599
00:37:02,910 --> 00:37:05,110
haven't seen each other for a long time.

600
00:37:07,870 --> 00:37:09,830
Jiu, I'm here to help you.

601
00:37:10,630 --> 00:37:12,760
To help you get rid of your loneliness.

602
00:37:13,350 --> 00:37:14,350
About your past,

603
00:37:14,870 --> 00:37:15,870
I've all known.

604
00:37:16,790 --> 00:37:18,310
I know how you feel.

605
00:37:20,630 --> 00:37:21,760
You're not dead yet,

606
00:37:22,750 --> 00:37:23,950
but you're not alive.

607
00:37:24,800 --> 00:37:26,260
Although you seems alive,

608
00:37:26,870 --> 00:37:28,400
your heart is already dead.

609
00:37:28,470 --> 00:37:29,470
I'm just like you.

610
00:37:32,430 --> 00:37:35,470
I mean I feel the same way as you.

611
00:37:36,430 --> 00:37:38,220
I can feel that loneliness.

612
00:37:41,020 --> 00:37:42,110
Hey, you.

613
00:37:42,440 --> 00:37:43,970
What are those sappy words?

614
00:37:44,990 --> 00:37:47,920
Between the lives of the tribe and Jiu,

615
00:37:48,070 --> 00:37:50,440
of course we choose the lives of the whole tribe.

616
00:37:50,440 --> 00:37:51,280
If you can be the one to choose,

617
00:37:51,280 --> 00:37:53,140
you'll certainly feel relieved.

618
00:37:53,430 --> 00:37:55,750
What if you are the chosen one?

619
00:37:57,230 --> 00:37:58,470
I... I'd like to.

620
00:37:58,750 --> 00:37:59,750
Really?

621
00:38:00,270 --> 00:38:01,670
We'll kill you now

622
00:38:02,030 --> 00:38:03,430
and save the whole tribe.

623
00:38:03,990 --> 00:38:04,990
Will you do it?

624
00:38:05,270 --> 00:38:07,070
Yes, I do.

625
00:38:07,220 --> 00:38:09,430
I'll strangle you to feed Jiu.

626
00:38:13,430 --> 00:38:16,550
All of you think you should sacrifice Jiu.

627
00:38:17,230 --> 00:38:19,260
You think your daughter

628
00:38:19,550 --> 00:38:21,810
should sacrifice for the whole village.

629
00:38:21,830 --> 00:38:22,830
And you.

630
00:38:23,180 --> 00:38:25,510
You think you should choose the majority.

631
00:38:26,390 --> 00:38:27,710
But there are not so many things

632
00:38:27,710 --> 00:38:29,570
that should be done in this world.

633
00:38:30,470 --> 00:38:32,070
You've all made your choice.

634
00:38:32,270 --> 00:38:34,070
She has to bear the consequences.

635
00:38:34,070 --> 00:38:35,070
Why?

636
00:38:35,790 --> 00:38:37,250
Just because it should be?

637
00:38:38,510 --> 00:38:40,590
Jiu lives in this dark cellar.

638
00:38:41,150 --> 00:38:42,790
She can't live or die.

639
00:38:43,430 --> 00:38:45,590
She can only depend on her mother

640
00:38:45,750 --> 00:38:47,680
to lure door-breakers to survive.

641
00:38:48,310 --> 00:38:50,390
Who wants to live like this?

642
00:38:50,470 --> 00:38:51,470
Anyone?

643
00:38:53,110 --> 00:38:54,750
It's all my fault.

644
00:38:56,670 --> 00:38:58,630
She has endured it for so many years.

645
00:38:58,630 --> 00:39:01,190
Do you think it'll pass in a word?

646
00:39:03,670 --> 00:39:05,470
I've made a choice.

647
00:39:06,280 --> 00:39:09,440
I'll kill myself to go with her.

648
00:39:09,670 --> 00:39:12,510
Didn't you make the coffin for me?

649
00:39:13,000 --> 00:39:15,130
Your daughter doesn't want you to die.

650
00:39:15,990 --> 00:39:18,120
She wants you to accompany her, Chief.

651
00:39:19,270 --> 00:39:21,270
Shouldn't you apologize to her?

652
00:39:21,990 --> 00:39:22,990
And you.

653
00:39:23,470 --> 00:39:24,470
As a mother,

654
00:39:24,510 --> 00:39:25,510
for your daughter,

655
00:39:25,510 --> 00:39:27,840
you shouldn't have killed so many people.

656
00:39:31,030 --> 00:39:34,150
All of you are making choices for Jiu.

657
00:39:34,870 --> 00:39:35,990
But did any of you

658
00:39:36,190 --> 00:39:38,150
care about her feelings

659
00:39:38,150 --> 00:39:39,280
and her loneliness?

660
00:39:45,470 --> 00:39:46,470
Jiu.

661
00:39:47,590 --> 00:39:48,590
I...

662
00:39:50,030 --> 00:39:51,150
I'm sorry.

663
00:39:56,470 --> 00:39:57,470
Jiu.

664
00:39:58,030 --> 00:39:59,390
We should...

665
00:39:59,620 --> 00:40:02,390
We should thank you.

666
00:40:03,390 --> 00:40:04,510
Jiu.

667
00:40:04,510 --> 00:40:06,140
Thank you.

668
00:40:06,140 --> 00:40:07,140
Thank you, Jiu.

669
00:40:07,310 --> 00:40:08,630
Thank you, Jiu.

670
00:40:09,270 --> 00:40:10,950
Thank you.

671
00:40:11,550 --> 00:40:13,110
Thank you so much.

672
00:40:13,190 --> 00:40:15,590
Thank you, Jiu.

673
00:40:19,580 --> 00:40:21,030
Thank you for saving us.
